============================================

Enable mod_rewrite

============================================

RewriteEngine On

============================================

Prevent directory browsing

============================================

Options -Indexes

============================================

Protect against DDoS by limiting request rates (requires mod_ratelimit)

NOTE: This works only if mod_ratelimit is enabled

============================================

 SetOutputFilter RATE_LIMIT SetEnv rate-limit 200 SetEnv rate-initial-burst 400

============================================

Block malicious user agents and bots

============================================

RewriteCond %{HTTP_USER_AGENT} (libwww-perl|wget|curl|spider|bot|crawler|slurp|nikto|scan) [NC,OR] RewriteCond %{HTTP_USER_AGENT} ^$ [OR] RewriteCond %{HTTP_USER_AGENT} (winhttp|sqlmap|python-requests) [NC] RewriteRule ^ - [F,L]

============================================

Prevent access to sensitive files

============================================

<FilesMatch ".(htaccess|htpasswd|ini|phps|log|cache)$"> Require all denied

============================================

Disable server signature

============================================

ServerSignature Off

============================================

Prevent hotlinking (allow your domains and portfolio domain)

============================================

Option 1: Allow specific domains (uncomment and add your portfolio domain)

RewriteCond %{HTTP_REFERER} !^$

RewriteCond %{HTTP_REFERER} !^https?://(www.)?(michitai.com|api.michitai.com|road.michitai.com|music.michitai.com|library.michitai.com|messenger.michitai.com|mutualluck.michitai.com|your-portfolio.com) [NC]

RewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} !^/logo.jpg$ [NC]

RewriteRule .(jpg|jpeg|png|gif|svg|mp4|webm)$ - [NC,F,L]

Option 2: Allow all referers for images (simpler, for testing or low-risk sites)

RewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} .(jpg|jpeg|png|gif|svg|mp4|webm)$ [NC] RewriteRule ^ - [L]

============================================

Enable compression for better performance

============================================

 AddOutputFilterByType DEFLATE text/plain AddOutputFilterByType DEFLATE text/html AddOutputFilterByType DEFLATE text/xml AddOutputFilterByType DEFLATE text/css AddOutputFilterByType DEFLATE application/xml AddOutputFilterByType DEFLATE application/xhtml+xml AddOutputFilterByType DEFLATE application/rss+xml AddOutputFilterByType DEFLATE application/javascript AddOutputFilterByType DEFLATE application/x-javascript

============================================

Set caching for static assets, including favicon

============================================

 ExpiresActive On ExpiresByType image/gif "access plus 1 month" ExpiresByType image/jpg "access plus 1 month" ExpiresByType image/jpeg "access plus 1 month" ExpiresByType image/png "access plus 1 month" ExpiresByType image/svg+xml "access plus 1 month" ExpiresByType image/x-icon "access plus 1 year" ExpiresByType text/css "access plus 1 month" ExpiresByType application/javascript "access plus 1 month"

============================================

Block common exploit attempts

============================================

RewriteCond %{QUERY_STRING} (eval(|base64_decode|system(|exec(|shell_exec() [NC,OR] RewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} (../|//|.php) [NC] RewriteRule ^ - [F,L]

============================================

Force HTTPS (requires SSL certificate)

============================================

RewriteCond %{HTTPS} off RewriteRule ^(.*)$ https://%{HTTP_HOST}%{REQUEST_URI} [L,R=301]

============================================

Image-specific headers (CORS and caching for all images)

============================================

<FilesMatch ".(jpg|jpeg|png|gif|svg)$"> Header set Cache-Control "public, max-age=31536000" Header set Access-Control-Allow-Origin "*"